      "name": "What is the difference between SVG and PNG transparency?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Both SVG and PNG support alpha-channel transparency. When you export an SVG with transparent areas to a transparent PNG, alpha information is preserved correctly. JPG would fill transparent areas with white." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
